    "Furthermore, considering our findings on both the strengths and limitations of using chatbots in design projects, it would be meaningful to examine the combined use of chatbots and surveys to leverage the advantages of both approaches.",
    "The present study has several limitations.",
    "First, the study participants were architecture students and faculty members proficient in verbally expressing design ideas, understanding what buildings require, and having outstanding novel ideas.",
    "This could have led to the creation of more topics and a higher topic and novelty rate than lay people.",
    "The second limitation is that the participants were aware that the project used in the present study was not real, and thus, their ideas would not be realized."
  ],
